  "description": "Top banner / header chrome for the Nordstrom Price Drop Shopping Bag email. Defines the shared global variables (UTM parameters and the utmLinkParams string that downstream fragments consume), the hidden preheader text, the 125th-anniversary top ticker, the Nordstrom logo (AEM media library), and the primary text navigation. Brand chrome images are AEM-hosted from folder nd_shopbag_pd.",
  "fragment": {
    "content": "<div class=\"acr-fragment is-locked has-html-params\" data-fragment-id=\"ajo:SELF\"><style acrite-mso-css=\"true\"></style><div class=\"acr-fragment acr-tmp-component\" data-tmp-component-id=\"html\" data-contenteditable=\"false\"><!-- BEGIN TOPBANNER -->\n{{!-- Global variables defined once here; later fragments consume utmLinkParams --}}\n{% let utmSource = \"N_triggered_bc\" %}\n{% let utmMedium = \"email\" %}\n{% let utmChannel = \"email_trig_ret_p\" %}\n{% let utmCampaign = \"n_shopbag_pd\" %}\n{% let utmTerm = profile._acssandboxustwo.nordstrom.identities.shopperId %}\n{% let utmDate = formatDate(getCurrentZonedDateTime(), \"yyyyMMdd\") %}\n{% let utmLinkParams = concat(\"utm_source=\", utmSource, \"&utm_medium=\", utmMedium, \"&utm_channel=\", utmChannel, \"&utm_campaign=\", utmCampaign, \"&utm_term=\", utmTerm, \"&utm_content=\", utmDate, \"_\") %}\n<span class=\"preheader\" style=\"display:none!important;visibility:hidden;opacity:0;color:transparent;height:0;width:0;font-size:1px;\">Shop now before it's gone.</span>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">\n  <!-- 125th ticker -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;\"><a data-nl-type=\"DEEPLINK\" data-tracking-type=\"DEEPLINK\" href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_ticker\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202940_25A_EmailShell_125th_topticker_mobile_desktop_2X.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:662a803b-d38f-4b7d-8df9-b8f9a414aac8\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Celebrating 125 years\" width=\"750\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;max-width:750px;height:auto;border:0;margin:0 auto;\"></a></td></tr>\n  <!-- logo -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:18px 20px 10px;\"><a data-nl-type=\"DEEPLINK\" data-tracking-type=\"DEEPLINK\" href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_logo\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com/content/dam/nd_shopbag_pd/202896_Nordstrom_Logo_Desktop_2x.gif\" data-medialibrary-id=\"urn:aaid:aem:477bcfbc-6f6f-4bef-802b-cfb4cd730471\" data-mediarepo-id=\"author-p69352-e612752.adobeaemcloud.com\" data-medialibrary-source=\"aem\" alt=\"Nordstrom\" width=\"220\" style=\"display:block;width:220px;max-width:60%;height:auto;border:0;margin:0 auto;\"></a></td></tr>\n  <!-- nav -->\n  <tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:6px 10px 16px;font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#111111;letter-spacing:.5px;\"><a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/designer?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_designer\" style=\"color:#111111;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;\">Designer</a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/women?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_women\" style=\"color:#111111;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;\">Women</a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/beauty?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_beauty\" style=\"color:#111111;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;\">Beauty</a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/men/shoes?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_shoes\" style=\"color:#111111;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;\">Shoes</a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/browse/sale?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_sale\" style=\"color:#b00000;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;font-weight:bold;\">Sale</a> <a href=\"https://www.nordstrom.com/stores?{{{utmLinkParams}}}pd_nav_stores\" style=\"color:#111111;text-decoration:none;padding:0 8px;\">Stores</a></td></tr>\n</table>\n<!-- END TOPBANNER --></div></div>",
